  <brief_title>The Effect of a Probiotic Preparation (VSL#3) Plus Infliximab in Children With Crohn's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reduction in Frequency of Infliximab Administration From q 8 Weeks to q 12 Weeks in Children With Crohn's Disease Receiving Probiotic VSL#3 Supplementation: A Pilot Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
