  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose was to evaluate as to whether administration of infliximab of 12 week interval
      with supplementary VSL#3 is more effective or at least of similar efficacy when compared to
      conventional administration of infliximab only of 8 week interval.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of our study was to evaluate if supplementation of VSL#3 can improve treatment
      outcome for those pediatric Crohn's patients treated with infliximab every 12 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
